  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Govt decides to set up parliamentary select committee to prepare new constitution - Justice Minister",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The inclusions made by the former President in the 22nd Amendment of the Constitution have been heavily criticized among the people. Therefore, I am going to submit the 22nd amendment to the Parliament next week, which has made amendments beyond the 19th by removing those additions. Also, the government has decided to form a parliamentary selection committee and prepare a new constitution, Justice Minister Wijetasa Rajapaksh said.",
        "He mentioned this while participating in the press conference held yesterday at the Ministry of Justice.",
        "The 22nd Amendment to the Constitution was earlier submitted to the Cabinet and gazetted with the approval of the Cabinet. However, the then President had incorporated some additions to the amendments.",
        "The appointments were widely criticized as reasserting the executive power of the President.",
        "However, now that the situation in the government has completely changed, I moved a proposal to the cabinet to remove the interpolations inserted by the former president in the 22nd amendment, reinstate the 19th amendment, remove some of the weaknesses in it, and submit a constitutional amendment that goes beyond the 19th.",
        "It has been forwarded to the Cabinet Office by the Act accordingly. After getting the approval of the cabinet next week, we are going to publish it through the gazette. I will take steps to submit it to the Parliament after 7 days of publication of the gazette notification.",
        "Also, the Chief Justice has confirmed that this 22nd Amendment Act is constitutional. Through this, we hope to propose amendments to the Constitution in a manner acceptable to all without arguments within the Parliament and among the civil organizations.",
        "And after the approval of the 22nd Amendment, the Cabinet has decided to establish a Parliamentary Select Committee and prepare a new constitution for the country through it.",
        "For that, our expectation is to get more support from the youth in the civil society and thereby prepare a constitution that can be accepted by the people of the country rather than the expectations of individuals.",
        "Similarly, I am going to make amendments in the Bribery Corruption Commission Bill and submit it to the Parliament as a Bill.",
        "I have appointed a committee headed by a High Court judge to prepare a law to remedy the deficiencies in this law. He said that he expects to submit this bill to the Parliament at the same time."
      ],
